text.section:
The application shall:
Be signed and verified by the applicant; and
Contain:
The name and address of the applicant;
The street address of the property on which the private group home is to be located or, if it has no street address, a description that identifies the property;
If the applicant does not own the property, the name of the owner;
A statement that the applicant will comply with the laws, rules, and regulations that relate to establishing and operating the private group home;
A statement that the applicant has sufficient financial resources to establish and operate the private group home or that those resources are available to the applicant; and
A description of the proposed program.
